item.title: CVE-2018-12416|2024-09-16T20:51:58.488Z -- tibco%20software%20inc. -- tibco%20datasynapse%20gridserver%20manager
item.description: The GridServer Broker and GridServer Director components of TIBCO Software Inc.'s TIBCO DataSynapse GridServer Manager contain vulnerabilities which may allow an unauthenticated user to perform cross-site request forgery (CSRF). Affected releases are TIBCO Software Inc. TIBCO DataSynapse GridServer Manager: versions up to and including 5.2.0; 6.0.0; 6.0.1; 6.0.2; 6.1.0; 6.1.1; 6.2.0; 6.3.0.
